Brilliant set of earnings fromHealthway Medical! 💉The increase in revenue of the Primary Healthcare Segment was on account ofrobust recovery in patient volume as compared to 1H-2020. This was further complemented byrevenue from the vaccination centers  COVID-19 Polymerase Chain Reaction (PCR) and serology-testing projects.Growth in revenue from this segment is 67.1%  similar and slightly better than that of Raffles Medical (65.4%)*Guidance*- Healthway Medical remains committed to safely administering the vaccines andreaching out to vulnerable segments of the communitythrough ourvaccination centers and mobile vaccination teams(This was announced by Govt in Jul likely we'll see this contribute to Q3 revenue)- Mandated all healthcare providers to issue digital pre-departure test (PDT).Healthway Medical currently offers PDTs at 33 of of our General Practitioner (“GP”) clinicsand issues digital PDT certificates to our patients.(Concurs with the MOH listwhere Healthway featured prominently as PCR  ART & PDT provider)-Recently opened a new health screening centre and a dental clinic in the Orchard Road area in July 2021and will continue to look for opportunities to grow its presence in the Primary and Specialist healthcare segments(A boost for their Specialist Healthcare segment as well  where revenue increased 21.7% as a result of pent-up demand for specialist healthcare services compared to 1H-2020)Hope this serves as the catalyst for Healthway to make a big move in the days ahead  looks like BBs accumulated quite a decent amount of 33/34. Cheers to all vested! 💪
